{\Large{\textbf{Preface}}}\\
In FDTD computation, due to the memory and run-time limitations it is required to use a FDTD computational domain as small as possible. For far-field pattern, in combine the FDTD computation near to far-field transformation is necessary. A brief review of the method to transform FDTD computed near-field data to far-field pattern of \cite{Taflove_book_05}, \cite{Mittra_CFDTD_04} is given here.\\
